# Drop CSVs here following the naming convention:
#
#   neuromotion_{category}_{subject_id}_{recording_id}.csv
#
# Supported categories:
#   n1       → Normal label 0
#   n2       → Normal label 0
#   spasms4  → Spasms label 1
#   spasms5  → Spasms label 1
#   hyper6   → Hypertonia label 2
#
# Each CSV must have columns matching BIOMARKER_NAMES in config.py
# (entropy, fractal_dim, kinetic_energy, root_stress, phase_x, phase_v,
#  mean_velocity, peak_frequency, angular_jerk) plus a 'timestamp' column.
